30:09.335 --> 30:13.822
under liberal arts at that point. There were 
really a lot of very major transitions that from my

30:14.883 --> 30:21.833
point of view occurred very smoothly. I didn't 
feel any great bumps in the road as we went along,

30:23.296 --> 30:39.139
